  "prompt": "What would be the Wipro joining dates for campus placed 2017 batch?",
  "response": "Wipro, like many other companies, typically communicates specific joining dates for campus recruits directly to the candidates through official channels such as email or their recruitment portal. For the 2017 batch, these dates would have been announced closer to the expected onboarding time, which can vary.\n\nHowever, based on general practices around that time, campus recruits from the 2017 batch might have been asked to join sometime between June and September 2017, depending on the company's project requirements and the completion of their academic commitments.\n\nIf you were part of the 2017 batch and placed at Wipro, you should refer to the communication you received directly from Wipro's HR department or check their recruitment portal for the most accurate and personalized information regarding your joining date.",
